{"id":"a72b2796-3022-4b49-a3f9-412b45eda70a","name":"Mikoto (Adrift)","description":"<p>The extremely affectionate queen of another Hoshido. She is a nurturing adoptive mother to <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a61ea8cd-5129-455e-8e0a-28932a1b31eb_character-azura\" target=\"_blank\">Azura</a>. Appears in Fire Emblem Fates.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">(I know it's the adrift version, but FEH doesn't act like it's any different than a base version.)</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8ceddBvsQXhh28GIStRqi.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hoshido is home to a woman who cares for all with affectionate, motherly devotion. That’s right, I’m talking about Mikoto!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/r6ck0UnIyxeIZmoQQR817.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mikoto took the throne after her husband, the late king Sumeragi, fell in the conflict with Nohr. As the Queen of Hoshido, she worked to protect her people and her beloved family.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/v4U-IB2J86ApQL64qkH2Z.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">She selflessly loved and cherished her children, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c6a936f1-1c7f-431d-9187-544f05cbb1f7_character-ryoma\" target=\"_blank\">Ryoma</a>, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/870a4c02-a46b-47ab-873a-e563e6147588_character-hinoka\" target=\"_blank\">Hinoka</a>, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1be22844-5eb6-4671-9058-b60d27b816ae_character-takumi\" target=\"_blank\">Takumi</a>, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bcd44453-0d64-403d-8a20-77ccb59e0915_character-sakura\" target=\"_blank\">Sakura</a>, and <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/849ecfd0-0788-4c97-9b16-e27a151449e0_character-corrin-male\" target=\"_blank\">Corrin</a>, and even <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a61ea8cd-5129-455e-8e0a-28932a1b31eb_character-azura\" target=\"_blank\">Azura</a>, who had been taken as a hostage from Nohr.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/b-Ysl1qa50grNwOT_9uhw.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Tragically, Mikoto perished while trying to protect <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/849ecfd0-0788-4c97-9b16-e27a151449e0_character-corrin-male\" target=\"_blank\">Corrin</a> during a certain incident. But her children took her wish for peace and kindness to heart, and carried it on into Hoshido’s future!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZYquC8YI21exHuCSCfvR2.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Full Art By: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://feheroes.fandom.com/wiki/Ito_Misei\" title=\"Ito Misei\" target=\"_blank\">Ito Misei (伊藤未生)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/v6Z5QwNoi-YccL3foRjte.webp\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"J-ADVa6IzsRlY6FqZx_kI.webp","creator":"Denki_The_Thunder_King27","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👑 Royalty","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":41,"messages":927,"created_at":"2026-05-10T23:20:42.206762+00:00"}